        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your suede sneakers, boots, and shoes looking their best with the GEAR AID Revivex Suede Shoe Cleaner and Conditioning Kit. This complete 2-pack care system restores and protects suede, nubuck, and Gore-Tex fabrics. Each kit includes a Boot and Shoe Cleaner (4 oz) to gently lift away dirt and grime, a PFAS-free Water Repellent (4 oz) to shield your footwear from moisture and stains, a stiff suede brush to remove embedded dirt and revive the nap, and a rubber eraser to reduce scuffs and marks. Use the cleaner to wash, the brush to lift dirt, the eraser to tackle stubborn scuffs, and the water repellent to protect—so your favorite shoes stay fresh, clean, and weather-ready. Made in the USA and safe for a wide range of materials, this unisex adult kit is the perfect solution for anyone who wants to extend the life and appearance of their suede footwear.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
